⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Lizaveta Ivanovna
node CRP · CRP · ⟦Lizaveta Ivanovna:CRP:7c3be3⟧

WHO   — Lizaveta Ivanovna — the gentle half-sister · the unplanned victim
WHAT  — The innocent the theory never counted: a gentle, simple woman, pregnant by some accounts, cut down because she was simply there.
WHERE — CRP · Crime and Punishment  Framework inputs: Crime and Punishment (Dostoevsky, 1866)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the ‘rational’ crime immediately produces a second, unplanned, indefensible death — the lie of the clean murder.
HOW   — By being in the wrong room at the wrong moment, and by the second swing of the axe.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  No theory had a place for me — I was the gentle one who simply walked in, and the clean crime needed two bodies after all.

